The paper deals with the fusion of data from multiple modalities, such as video, speech, and text, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed techniques on tasks related to machine translation (cs.CL) and emotion recognition (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.CL, and cs.LG, followed by cs.MM and cs.AI.
